{
  "stem": "13851.1",
  "chunk_idx": 4,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 7.5,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 32,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "We went with our religious teacher, and-- and other kids went with the-- with the [? father, ?] the Christians.",
      "word_count": 20
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 33,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "So we had separated that time.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 33,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "I'm remembering very good.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 33,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "I remember exactly what we learned about all history about Jewish history and-- and religion.",
      "word_count": 15
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 33,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "Did you ever experience any anti-Semitism as a child?",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 34,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Yes, I experienced a lot of anti-Semitic experiences.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 34,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "When I went to cheder-- and at that time, when I went home, and at the time, the church was not far from the market where the cheder was.",
      "word_count": 29
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 34,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "I was always hit in-- I was hit in the back.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 34,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "Somebody would run into me and was hitting me.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 34,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "I always came up crying.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 34,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "I was hit, and I didn't know why, what reason I was hit.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 34,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "But that was anti-Semitic.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 34,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "And other things-- I remember in the summertime, there was a-- a lake at our town.",
      "word_count": 16
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 34,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 8,
      "text": "And we used to go swimming.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 34,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 9,
      "text": "And it was separate.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 34,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 10,
      "text": "They separated us.",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 34,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 11,
      "text": "We couldn't swim with the Gentiles in same-- same river.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 34,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 12,
      "text": "So we had, like, a Jewish special place to go.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 34,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 13,
      "text": "And a lot of times, in there, they were throwing stones at us when we went through to get lake.",
      "word_count": 20
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 34,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 14,
      "text": "So it was very bad experience, yeah.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 35,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "It was terrible that we lived, and we have to take it.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 35,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "We can't do, because-- because there was-- nobody would help us to-- to clear this up and to do something for it.",
      "word_count": 22
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 35,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "Because it's-- it's in that-- and the people [INAUDIBLE] in that anti-Semitic things that they-- what they couldn't do anything about it.",
      "word_count": 22
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 35,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "So they'd be very, like, accustomed to it.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 35,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "It's supposed to be like that.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 36,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Yeah, we had friends-- nice, very nice people and weren't Jewish, yeah.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 36,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "Very, very close friends, yeah.",
      "word_count": 5
    }
  ],
